{"root":{"data":{"text":"软件工程"},"children":[{"data":{"text":"软件工程定义"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoi5guwn9s0","created":1775725490887,"text":"由方法、工具和过程三个部分组成"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi5oka3hc0","created":1775725507658,"text":"PDCA（Plan、Do、Check、Action）"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi6obiu6w0","created":1775725585493,"text":"软件开发方法"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoi6s8pvqw0","created":1775725594031,"text":"形式化方法"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoi6yv7iao0","created":1775725608451,"text":"净室软件工程CSE"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoi76pvgi80","created":1775725625543,"text":"函数理论（记忆：玩一阵）","note":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoi8c67cio0","created":1775725715778,"text":"完备性"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi8dqit2w0","created":1775725719184,"text":"一致性"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi8fh4se80","created":1775725722969,"text":"正确性"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi7c5cwx40","created":1775725637363,"text":"抽样理论"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi8lblx740","created":1775725735696,"text":"限制"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoi8n3iio80","created":1775725739560,"text":"对工程师要求高"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi8p6awrc0","created":1775725744082,"text":"不依赖传统单元测试不实际"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi8w4921c0","created":1775725759196,"text":"属于传统软件工程体系，无法解决所有工程问题"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi97ptu7c0","created":1775725784445,"text":"逆向工程（记忆：世仇结、分工龄）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoi9r2ub8g0","created":1775725826591,"text":"实现级"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoia696xb40","created":1775725859627,"text":"跟代码相关，比如抽象语法树、符号表等"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi9tfra4g0","created":1775725831725,"text":"结构级"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoiaht5wjk0","created":1775725884779,"text":"跟程序分量相关，比如掉用途、结构图等"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi9x2tgtc0","created":1775725839650,"text":"功能级"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoiap3zk9s0","created":1775725900671,"text":"程序段功能与程序段关系"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoi9zsscv40","created":1775725845574,"text":"领域级"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoib0uz48g0","created":1775725926247,"text":"程序实体与应用领域对应关系"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoib8d1nl40","created":1775725942577,"text":"再工程"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoibazyem80","created":1775725948316,"text":"逆向工程 + 新需求 + 正向工程"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoibtr4hyo0","created":1775725989141,"text":"基于构建的软件工程（CBSE）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoic2jytc00","created":1775726008299,"text":"特性（记忆：竹鼠挡毒标）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoicezj36o0","created":1775726035362,"text":"可组装性"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoidh6ltns0","created":1775726118507,"text":"外部交互必须通过公开定义接口进行，必须提供对自身信息的外部访问，例如方法和属性"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoickvfcl40","created":1775726048174,"text":"可部署性"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoido6uvgo0","created":1775726133760,"text":"构件需要自包含，必须能作为一个独立的实体运行。总是二进制格式，无须在部署前编译。如果构建实现为一项服务，应由服务提供者来部署"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoicmzt4v40","created":1775726052793,"text":"文档化"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoidrh1zmg0","created":1775726140907,"text":"必须完全文档化，这样用户能确定是否构件满足需求，应定义所有接口的语法及语义"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoicoa42540","created":1775726055594,"text":"独立性"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoidu8jrhc0","created":1775726146923,"text":"可以在无其它特殊构件的情况下进行组装和部署"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoicocx3u80","created":1775726055762,"text":"标准化"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoie2636zc0","created":1775726164188,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoie2dools0","created":1775726164648,"text":"构件必须符合某种标准化的构件模型，此模型定义构件接口、构件元数据、文档管理、组成以及部署"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoicsl362g0","created":1775726064963,"text":"可见性"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoie570fh40","created":1775726170775,"text":"没有（外部）可见状态（两个特殊情况：1. 构件本身不直接暴露状态，但可以通过运行时容器管理状态并对外提供可见性；2. 对于不影响构件功能的某些属性可以对外部可见）"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoie9vzcfs0","created":1775726180992,"text":"分类（记忆：独显时装秀）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoieh48ylc0","created":1775726196729,"text":"独立而成熟的构件"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoien5175k0","created":1775726209837,"text":"成熟度高，比如数据库系统，操作系统等"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoieorkt4g0","created":1775726213377,"text":"有限制的构件"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoietl99nk0","created":1775726223879,"text":"可能会产生冲突，需测试后使用，比如各种基础类库"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoievb2h4w0","created":1775726227616,"text":"适应性构件"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoif1l0nqg0","created":1775726241279,"text":"通过包装或接口技术处理了不兼容、资源冲突等问题，可直接在各种环境中使用，例如ActiveX组件"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoif3phgio0","created":1775726245902,"text":"装配的构件"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoif8a5km00","created":1775726255859,"text":"需要使用胶水代码进行连接"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoifcvylyw0","created":1775726265885,"text":"可修改的构件"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoifhycuso0","created":1775726276914,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoifi5k35s0","created":1775726277349,"text":"可修改错误、增加新功能，通过重新“包装”或接口实现构件版本替换"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoifl15j540","created":1775726283613,"text":"主要活动"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoifodmfqo0","created":1775726290897,"text":"面向复用的开发"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoifr0x3dc0","created":1775726296660,"text":"基于复用的开发"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoifxspvy80","created":1775726311401,"text":"系统需求概览"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoig5u4b140","created":1775726328901,"text":"识别候选构件"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoig8lp1sg0","created":1775726334921,"text":"根据发现的构件修改需求"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoigbado1s0","created":1775726340767,"text":"体系结构设计"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoigfeby340","created":1775726349713,"text":"构件的定制和适配"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoigix20e80","created":1775726357376,"text":"构件组装，创建系统"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoignta38g0","created":1775726368032,"text":"分类"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoigroki1s0","created":1775726376454,"text":"顺序组装"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoigvlf4yg0","created":1775726384971,"text":"叠加组装"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoigy800600","created":1775726390689,"text":"层次组装"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoigoo3z5k0","created":1775726369896,"text":"不兼容"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoih2zaq4g0","created":1775726401047,"text":"参数不兼容"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoihc2rpbs0","created":1775726420848,"text":"操作名相同，参数不同"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoih52473k0","created":1775726405571,"text":"操作不兼容"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoihhck9z40","created":1775726432324,"text":"操作名不同"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoih7tm5m00","created":1775726411587,"text":"操作不完备"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoihkea7j40","created":1775726438959,"text":"一个构件提供的“接口”是另一个构件“请求”的子集，或相反"},"children":[]}]}]}]}]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoik77qh340","created":1775726645357,"text":"软件过程/开发/生命周期模型"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoik9ex0b40","created":1775726650145,"text":"路径"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoikbtb5ko0","created":1775726655369,"text":"软件定义"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoikd16ozc0","created":1775726658022,"text":"软件开发"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoikebzkl40","created":1775726660852,"text":"软件运行"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoikg3cdio0","created":1775726664682,"text":"软件维护"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoikh2x4ug0","created":1775726666834,"text":"软件淘汰"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoikoxyvyo0","created":1775726683948,"text":"分类"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoikq92nco0","created":1775726686797,"text":"瀑布模型"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoikv1huu80","created":1775726697222,"text":"将开发过程分为需求分析、软件设计、软件实现、单元测试（单元测试，集成测试，系统测试）、运行维护几个阶段"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoikvvczao0","created":1775726699028,"text":"不能适应需求变化，适合需求完全确定的项目"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoikzk5ys80","created":1775726707058,"text":"原型模型/演化模型/快速原型模型"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoil5y8t000","created":1775726720970,"text":"适用于需求难以完整定义的软件开发，根据用户反馈不断改进、迭代直至形成最终产品"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoilbvwr280","created":1775726733890,"text":"增量模型"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoilfl9pcw0","created":1775726741954,"text":"把系统分为多个模块，按模块顺序开发"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoimkgjwdc0","created":1775726830917,"text":"螺旋模型（快速原型 + 风险分析）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoimrjh6n40","created":1775726846331,"text":"适用于庞大、复杂且具有高风险的系统"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoimun7kts0","created":1775726853087,"text":"喷泉模型"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoimwru3sw0","created":1775726857720,"text":"以对象为驱动，面向对象的软件开发模型"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoin000zkw0","created":1775726864746,"text":"V模型"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoiojn99vk0","created":1775726985874,"text":"需求分析、概要设计、详细设计、编码"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoiopmqa1k0","created":1775726998902,"text":"验收测试、系统测试、集成测试、单元测试"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoiowrm7k80","created":1775727014435,"text":"单元测试 依赖 详细设计"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoip0e790w0","created":1775727022331,"text":"集成测试 依赖 概要设计"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoip404sso0","created":1775727030188,"text":"系统测试 依赖 需求分析"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoip7qcmwo0","created":1775727038303,"text":"验收测试 依赖 用户需求"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoipng3bqo0","created":1775727072512,"text":"统一过程模型RUP"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoipqkhizs0","created":1775727079308,"text":"用例驱动的、以体系结构为中心的、迭代和增量的软件开发模型"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoipzmchps0","created":1775727099011,"text":"4+1视图"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoiq38bits0","created":1775727106870,"text":"逻辑视图"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoiq4frnk80","created":1775727109497,"text":"实现视图"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoiq5hy19c0","created":1775727111806,"text":"进程视图"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoiq6sb8680","created":1775727114609,"text":"部署视图"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoiq8da0800","created":1775727118054,"text":"+1 用例"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoiqeje3zc0","created":1775727131484,"text":"生命周期（记忆：建需分食测，部配变项环）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoiqq1t8740","created":1775727156543,"text":"业务建模"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoiqsflbwg0","created":1775727161729,"text":"需求"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoiqtnmgk00","created":1775727164392,"text":"分析与设计"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoiqveqaqo0","created":1775727168208,"text":"实现"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoiqwgpdzs0","created":1775727170504,"text":"测试"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoir1n2nrs0","created":1775727181773,"text":"部署"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoir2yymaw0","created":1775727184668,"text":"配置与变更管理"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoir5xolu00","created":1775727191121,"text":"项目挂历"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoir71k35c0","created":1775727193533,"text":"环境"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoirbb50io0","created":1775727202819,"text":"敏捷方法"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoire82c9s0","created":1775727209163,"text":"宣言"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoirfy7liw0","created":1775727212921,"text":"个体和交互胜过过程和工具"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoiri5pzww0","created":1775727217729,"text":"可工作的软件胜过大量的文档"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoirku9wiw0","created":1775727223567,"text":"客户合作胜过合同谈判"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoirn7c98o0","created":1775727228711,"text":"响应变化胜过遵循计划"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoirrp2o400","created":1775727238490,"text":"适用场景"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoirv5icjk0","created":1775727246014,"text":"规模小"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoirxxrw0w0","created":1775727252077,"text":"变化快"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhois1g5o680","created":1775727259719,"text":"方法"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhois2e9feo0","created":1775727261781,"text":"极限编程xp"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhois4we1xk0","created":1775727267231,"text":"水晶系列"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhois7lb3140","created":1775727273091,"text":"以人为中"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhoisalbzc80","created":1775727279623,"text":"scrum"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoise79qdc0","created":1775727287480,"text":"角色"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhoisgyjp9c0","created":1775727293482,"text":"产品负责人"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoisihixs00","created":1775727296807,"text":"敏捷教练"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhoiskkqnxk0","created":